              "settings": {
                "editor": "<h5 class=\"mb-2 whitespace-pre-line last:mb-0\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>About VSF and Our Mission</strong></h5><p class=\"mb-2 whitespace-pre-line last:mb-0\">Q: What is Vetiver Sans Frontieres (VSF)?</p><p class=\"mb-2 whitespace-pre-line last:mb-0\">A: VSF is a Canadian-based charity that specializes in implementing Vetiver Grass Technology (VGT) for environmental conservation and land rehabilitation in tropical and subtropical countries. We work to create sustainable environmental solutions while supporting local communities.</p><p class=\"mb-2 whitespace-pre-line last:mb-0\">Q: How does VSF make a difference?</p><p class=\"mb-2 whitespace-pre-line last:mb-0\">A: Our work creates multiple positive impacts:</p><ul><li>Environmental: Reduces soil loss by 90% and water runoff by 70%</li><li>Economic: Provides income opportunities for rural communities through handicrafts and essential oil production</li><li>Cost-effective: Implements solutions that are 85% more cost-effective than traditional methods</li><li>Sustainable: Creates long-term impact with minimal maintenance needs</li></ul><p class=\"mb-2 whitespace-pre-line last:mb-0\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Donation Information</strong></p><p class=\"mb-2 whitespace-pre-line last:mb-0\">Q: How can I donate to VSF?</p><p class=\"mb-2 whitespace-pre-line last:mb-0\">A: You can make a secure donation through our official platform, Zeffy <a href=\"https://www.zeffy.com/donation-form/cbac2a62-15cb-4f94-866c-c860b1cfa606\">by clicking here</a>. We accept various payment methods, and you'll receive an immediate tax receipt for your contribution.</p><p class=\"mb-2 whitespace-pre-line last:mb-0\">Q: How are my donations used?</p><p class=\"mb-2 whitespace-pre-line last:mb-0\">A: Your donations directly support:</p><ul><li>Implementation of Vetiver Grass Technology projects</li><li>Training programs for local communities</li><li>Infrastructure support in project areas</li><li>Environmental design and consultation services</li></ul><p class=\"mb-2 whitespace-pre-line last:mb-0\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Impact and Accountability</strong></p><p class=\"mb-2 whitespace-pre-line last:mb-0\">Q: How do I know my donation makes an impact?</p><p class=\"mb-2 whitespace-pre-line last:mb-0\">A: VSF maintains transparency in our operations by:</p><ul><li>Partnering with respected organizations like The Vetiver Network International (TVNI)</li><li>Providing measurable impact metrics (soil loss reduction, water conservation)</li><li>Documenting project outcomes and community benefits</li><li>Regular updates through our social media channels and email newsletter</li></ul>"
              },
